                               Version 3

 Version 3 has a number of new functions:-

         1: The build program is a lot more flexible:-

                  1: You can merge a LST file from a LIB.
                  2: Merge a LST file from disk.
                  3: Save part of a listing to disk.
                  4: Save part of a listing directly to a LIB.

         2: You can now make a LIB type file from any ascii files. This is
            good for storage of a number of related files.


